<name>WINDOW DEFOGGER SYSTEM</name>
<para id="RM0000020LP002X" category="J" type-id="304X8" name-id="WS0UJ-01" from="200601">
<dtccode/>
<dtcname>Rear Window Defogger System does not Operate</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM0000020LP002X_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___000058J00000">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>When the rear window defogger switch, which is built into the heater control assembly, is operated, the operation signals are transmitted to the A/C amplifier assembly through LIN. When the A/C amplifier assembly receives the signals, it turns on the DEFOG relay to operate the rear window defogger.</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
